{"name":"Smashed Potatoes","slug":"smashed-potatoes","description":"<p>Crazy crispy on the outside and fluffy on the inside.&nbsp;Perfect side to add to your holiday dinner—a change from the classic mashed potatoes!</p>","ingredients":[{"name":"mixed baby potatoes","quantity":"1 lb (450 g)","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"unsalted butter or olive oil","quantity":"2 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Holiday Seasoning","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Roasted Garlic Aioli","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":"prepared"},{"name":"Roasted Garlic Aioli Mix","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"light mayonnaise","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"lemon juice","quantity":"1 tsp","additionalInstruction":"optional"}],"totalTime":"23 minutes","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Preheat oven to 425° F (220° C). Line a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://epicure.com/en-ca/product/1006105\">Sheet Pan</a>&nbsp;with a&nbsp;<a data-item-id=\"457bbcd8-77a0-4a70-96c9-951018a3fc9c\" href=\"\">Sheet Pan Liner</a>.</li>\n  <li>Place potatoes in a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://epicure.com/en-ca/product/1004235\">Multipurpose Steamer</a>. Microwave on high, with lid on, for 6–8 minutes.</li>\n  <li>Add butter and gently toss to coat. Spread potatoes in a single layer on baking sheet.</li>\n  <li>Using a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://epicure.com/en-ca/product/1004242\">Prep Bowl</a>&nbsp;or glass, smash each potato to about <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub>” thickness.</li>\n  <li>Sprinkle with seasoning and bake for 10 minutes, flipping once.</li>\n  <li>Once baked, drizzle with Aioli and serve hot.</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"sides","name":"Side Dishes"},{"slug":"vegetarian","name":"Vegetarian"},{"slug":"christmas","name":"Christmas"},{"slug":"dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"epic_life_dinner","name":"Dinner"},{"slug":"sheet_pan_3e5bebd","name":"Sheet Pan"},{"slug":"low_sodi